snippet.title: Hot Wheels Stunt Driver - COMPLETE PLAYTHROUGH
snippet.description:
This is one of the best games EVER made(Yes, that's the nostalgia talking), and since there are next to no videos about it on YouTube, I thought it would have been a good idea to record THE WHOLE GAME.

This video contains:
-Full championship mode
-The hidden Planet level
-Example of custom track

Total crashes: 2

Timestamps:
0:00 - Intro
1:12 - The kitchen/Living room
4:12 - The bedroom
6:38 - The greenhouse
9:09 - The attic
11:12 - The sandbox
14:50 - The casino
18:06 - The planet
21:09 - Custom track building
22:29 - Custom track
